overview:
Technology , Trends & news - WHERE IS THE FUTURE OF TECHNOLOGY, COMPUTING AND THE INTERNET HEADED ?

JTN- Network is a networked blog , Registration is open and free, for any who would like a blog @JTN-network, or Contributor , Reviewer , or for Press Release ..

Basically retired then site was started generally to fill time and see what interest there might be in vision which continues to develop as we move go on over the last year we have had many ups and downs loss of data and data bases as we move along testing ..

as the visitor numbers began to increase , it was decided to register a TLD and hosing for the Blog we are still technically testing formats and design though always amazed at how the following has jumped over the last year from an average of 50 to 100 unique visits a month to 6000 unique visitors a month and nearly 700 syndicated articles & Press releases in the last month on around 80 news tech and gadget blogs and E zines ..

The gold to fill Time Productively and Have fun, Income was never on the list if the site earns something great if not well someone with plenty of wisdom once told me ” you can Never miss what you never had ”
